com.hexaware.entity

Class Evidence

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hexaware.entity.Evidence

  • public class Evidence
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents evidence related to an incident.

    An instance of this class contains information about the evidence, including its ID, description, location where it was found, and the ID of the incident it is associated with.
